    Test if a value is an array-like object containing only functions.

    Parameters
    ----------
    value: any
        value to test.

    Returns
    -------
    y: boolean
        boolean indicating if value is an array-like object containing only functions.

    Examples
    --------
    > function beep(){};
    > function boop(){};
    > var bool = {{alias}}( [ beep, boop ] )
    true

    > bool = {{alias}}( [ {}, beep ] )
    false
